<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0068b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0068b0101">夫玄捴妙寂。炁末世<note n="0068001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30519"/>＝所【史】</note><app n="0068001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30519"/></rdg></app>能顯
<lb ed="I" n="0068b02" type="honorific"/>其元。真景疑槨。非季俗之<app type="star" corresp="#0068001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30519"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0068b03" type="honorific"/>宣其皇。是以鉢若之智難昇
<lb ed="I" n="0068b04" type="honorific"/>岨皆之葙。故<note n="0068002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30520"/>＝顯【史】</note><app n="0068002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30520"/></rdg></app>神<g ref="#CB30521"/>歸敬慈
<lb ed="I" n="0068b05" type="honorific"/>萇者矣。但聖藏淟澄洪<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">臨</unclear>道
<lb ed="I" n="0068b06" type="honorific"/>一炁可寶塔云重菒<g ref="#CB30522"/>寶輻
<lb ed="I" n="0068b07" type="honorific"/>海臻。溸像寸暈則無牛号之
<lb ed="I" n="0068b08" type="honorific"/>潤<note n="0068003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30523"/>＝哉【史】</note><app n="0068003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">哉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30523"/></rdg></app>。山岳摧巔。海獲崩竭。偘
<lb ed="I" n="0068b09" type="honorific"/>神儀於清流之曲。葵永顏不
<lb ed="I" n="0068b10" type="honorific"/>朽者也。<note n="0068004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30524"/>＝豈【史】</note><app n="0068004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">豈</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30524"/></rdg></app>緣<note n="0068005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30525"/>＝微【史】</note><app n="0068005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30525"/></rdg></app>工。當願正<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">備</unclear>。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b11" type="honorific"/>遠通慈<note n="0068006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">朖＝朗【史】</note><app n="0068006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朖</rdg></app>。垢於<note n="0068007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𩇕＝青【史】</note><app n="0068007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">青</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩇕</rdg></app>宮。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b12" type="honorific"/>上為皇帝　陛下。國督祚康。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b13" type="honorific"/>祚幾標式。合右拙塢村。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">返</unclear>願
<lb ed="I" n="0068b14" type="honorific"/>合邑七十人等。敬造室家石
<lb ed="I" n="0068b15" type="honorific"/>像一區。直鍾薩提。願合邑<note n="0068008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30526"/>＝仰【史】</note><app n="0068008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">仰</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30526"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0068b16" type="honorific"/>隊七世。乃至<app type="star" corresp="#0068001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30519"/></rdg></app>生。朋<note n="0068009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㕛＝友【史】</note><app n="0068009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">友</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㕛</rdg></app>眷屬。
<lb ed="I" n="0068b17" type="honorific"/>合霜奢梨。普洽私願。一時成
<lb ed="I" n="0068b18" type="honorific"/>佛。　　天寶二年保莊嚴功德飛騎尉杜思福邑子董
<lb ed="I" n="0068b19" type="honorific"/>建儀元年歲在毋申六月丁
<lb ed="I" n="0068b20" type="honorific"/>亥朔廿八日甲寅日
<lb ed="I" n="0068b21" type="honorific"/>願□主施□□</p>
